        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "1. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Sign Up and Explore the Dashboard",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Head to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "monday.com",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " and create a free account. Once logged in, you're greeted with a clean dashboard where you can start from scratch or pick from over 200 templates—perfect for industries like marketing, construction, or agile teams.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "2. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Create Your First Board",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Click 'Add' to create a new board. Think of boards as your project command center. For example, I set up a 'Content Calendar' board to track blog posts, using columns for status, due dates, and assignees. This visual setup eliminates guesswork.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "3. ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Customize Columns and Views",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": monday.com offers 8 column types in the free plan, like text, numbers, and status. Add columns to fit your workflow—such as a dropdown for priority levels. Switch between views like Kanban or timeline to see your project from different angles.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
